{"tid":2395283,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個尼馬做唔到球王嘅原因","createTime":"2021-02-04T20:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T03:55:57.000Z","uid":186431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e4372000a6c3ceb4d188abcec8d0c9a491d0b311","tid":2395283,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T20:15:39.000Z","msg":"尼馬：英超「埋身肉搏」嚇親我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tAJwKzA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtAJwKzA.jpg&h=2dcbaf26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now Sports】尼馬指英超風格太多身體接觸，是他沒有選擇到英超發展的原因之一。<br />\n尼馬（Neymar）接受英國《每日郵報》訪問時，稱自己被英超嚇得卻步的箇中原因：「我沒有看過太多英超比賽，但我經常聽聞在比賽中有很多身體接觸。當然法甲都有！」他更指出2020似乎打破了不少人的希望與打算，所以他更為珍惜自己擁有的一切，希望全力為PSG奪下歐聯，更想為巴西取得世界盃。<br />\n<br />\n尼馬在場上不時成為敵方球員追擊的目標，更曾因此而多次受傷，難免抗拒粗野踢法。有報道指，29歲的尼馬除了沒有打算轉戰英超，更已準備好長線留在法甲發展，有望跟巴黎聖日耳門續簽4年新約。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP<br />\n<br />\n吹大咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc9abebe5a4c34bc4cc34756e54672cc7bf27a4d","tid":2395283,"uid":366500,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T20:21:13.000Z","msg":"They see me rolling<br />\nThey hating <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/CorruptSentimentalAsianconstablebutterfly-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FCorruptSentimentalAsianconstablebutterfly-size_restricted.gif&h=49125058&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"655ac11e7952ff241f6c72ddb66616e8b840195a","tid":2395283,"uid":186431,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"cc9abebe5a4c34bc4cc34756e54672cc7bf27a4d","tid":2395283,"uid":366500,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T20:21:13.000Z","msg":"They see me rolling<br />\nThey hating <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/CorruptSentimentalAsianconstablebutterf